                </names>
                <summary>Nancy Hagan, age 46, died in Burlington, IA, on 10/15/1857. Widow of Levi
                    Hagan, Esq. Born in Chambersburg, PA, later moved to Staunton. Married at young
                    age to Henry Snydor, and moved to Hamilton, OH, where husband died in 1840.
                    Moved to Burlington in 1843, where she married Hagen in same year. Member of
                    local Methodist Church.</summary>
            </div>
